{% extends "templates/base.njk" %}
{% block content %}
<div class="sb-page-head">
    <h1 class="sb-page-title">No bot connected</h1>
    <p class="sb-page-subtitle">The panel is running, but no trading bot has connected over IPC yet.</p>
</div>
<div class="sb-console-card">
    <h2>Windows (D:\panel + D:\tf2autobot)</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Run <code>.\setup-bot.ps1</code> from the panel folder (once).</li>
        <li>Start the <strong>panel</strong> first: <code>node dist/server/index.js</code></li>
        <li>Start the <strong>bot</strong>: <code>cd D:\tf2autobot</code> then <code>node dist/app.js</code></li>
        <li>Bot <code>.env</code> must have <code>IPC=true</code> and <code>TLS=false</code>.</li>
        <li>Your SteamID64 must be in bot <code>ADMINS=</code> to use the panel.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Status: <a href="/health/bot">/health/bot</a> — reload this page after the bot connects.</p>
</div>
{% endblock %}
